(9540, -1, 'album_switchtype_album_thumbpath_text', 'cphelptext', 'This is the path where your thumbnails are being stored. Unlike the "Full Picture File Path" setting, this path <strong>must</strong> be within your web root. Users will need to be able to access the files in this directory directly.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIt must be writeable by PHP. The easiest way to do this is CHMOD it 777 (consult your FTP, Telnet, or SSH documentation for more info on how to do this).', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 1193056102, '3.7.0 Beta 1'),
