(9610, -1, 'attachment_intro_downloadsless_text', 'cphelptext', 'Finds attachments that have had less than X downloads, X being the number you specify. Note if you use both More Than and Less Than X Downloads, the More Than number must be less than the Less Than number or there will be no search range!', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 0, ''),
