(9934, -1, 'email_genlist_start_postsupper_text', 'cphelptext', 'The user must have less than this number of posts in order to be found. This criteria can be used in conjunction with the Number of Posts is Greater Than or Equal To criteria. Keep in mind that if you do use both, this number must be MORE than the Number of Posts is Greater Than number for any users to be found! (see <a href="help.php?do=answer&amp;page=email&amp;pageaction=genlist&amp;option=postslower">Number of Posts is Greater Than or Equal To</a>)', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 1205431035, '3.7.0 Release Candidate 1'),
