(9956, -1, 'email_genlist_start_ipaddress_text', 'cphelptext', 'Enter a number in this field to search by IP address. It can be a full IP address (such as 24.23.120.15) or a partial (such as 24.23.120). In the case of a partial, it would match users with any number(s) for the last block.', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 0, ''),
