(10126, -1, 'forumpermission_edit_quickforum_canseedelnotice_text', 'cphelptext', 'If this is set to Yes, this group will be able to see deletion notices in this forum. Deletion notices are what is left behind after a user deletes a post or thread. Moderators will always be able to see deletion notices in forums they moderate - this setting does not affect them.', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 0, ''),
