(10128, -1, 'forumpermission_edit_quickforum_cansearch_text', 'cphelptext', 'If this is set to No, the user will not be allowed to search this forum, even if they can view it or perform other actions in it. It will not appear in the list of forums to search from on the search screen, and it will not be included if the user opts to search all forums.', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 0, ''),
