(10130, -1, 'forumpermission_edit_quickforum_canemail_text', 'cphelptext', 'If this is set to No, the user will not be allowed to use the Email to Friend feature (which is linked from the bottom of every thread). This setting is disregarded if you have set Email Functions to Off under general options - no one would be allowed to use Email to Friend in that case.', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 0, ''),
