(10132, -1, 'forumpermission_edit_quickforum_cangetattachment_text', 'cphelptext', 'If this is set to No, users will not be allowed to download post attachments from threads in this forum. The link will still appear but they will be told, after clicking on it, that they don''t have permission.', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 0, ''),
