(10136, -1, 'forumpermission_edit_quickforum_canreplyown_text', 'cphelptext', 'If this is set to No, users will not be able to reply to threads that they are the first poster in (started the thread). If you have Can post new threads set to No above, this setting is irrelevant.', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 0, ''),
