(10140, -1, 'forumpermission_edit_quickforum_followforummoderation_text', 'cphelptext', 'If this is set to No, when a user from this group posts in this forum, their post will be put in the moderator queue regardless of whether or not you have turned on the moderator queue for this forum.', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 0, ''),
