(10650, -1, 'options_options_tagcloud_searchcloud_text', 'cphelptext', 'If you enable this option, a new tag cloud will be shown at the bottom of the advanced search page. This tag cloud differs from the version <a href="../tags.php" target="_blank">here</a> because it is based on the amount of searches done for a particular tag instead of the number of times the tag is used.', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 1206528776, '3.7.0 Release Candidate 2'),
