(10652, -1, 'options_options_tagcloud_searchhistory_text', 'cphelptext', 'The number of days that tag searching information should be stored for. This information is used to build the tag cloud.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n0 will keep data around permanently.', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 1206528207, '3.7.0 Release Candidate 2'),
