(10690, -1, 'options_options_bbactive_text', 'cphelptext', 'If this is set to "Yes", then users will be able to use your forum. If this is set to "No", then users will see a message notifying them that the forum is turned off.  You can edit this message in the "Reason For Turning Forum Off" option below.<br /><br />\r\n\r\nNote that admins will still be able to use the forum while it is off, but they will see a notice on the top and bottom of the screen that says the forum is offline.', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 0, ''),
