(10772, -1, 'options_options_dstonoff_text', 'cphelptext', 'If the time zone for the Default Time Zone Offset is currently in Daylight Savings time, set this to Yes. Remember, this only affects guests and those not logged in. Registered, logged-in users can set their own DST options in their User CP.', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 0, ''),
