(10776, -1, 'options_options_timeformat_text', 'cphelptext', 'This is the format in which the time is presented on all vBulletin pages. It uses PHP''s <a href="http://www.php.net/date" target="_blank">date function formatting options</a>.<br /><br />\r\n\r\nSome examples:<br />\r\n<b>h:i A</b> becomes 11:15 PM<br />\r\n<b>H:i</b> becomes 23:15', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 0, ''),
