(10780, -1, 'options_options_calformat1_text', 'cphelptext', 'When a user provides their birth date, including year, it will be shown in their profile. This is the format of the date that will be shown. It follows PHP''s <a href="http://www.php.net/date" target="_blank">date function formatting options</a>. You should not enter any time formatting options.', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 0, ''),
