(10782, -1, 'options_options_calformat2_text', 'cphelptext', 'When a user provides their birth date it will be shown in their profile. This is the format of the date that will be shown when the user provides the month and day but not the year. It follows PHP''s <a href="http://www.php.net/date" target="_blank">date function formatting options</a>. You should not enter any time formatting options, and you should <b>not</b> enter any year code.', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 0, ''),
