(11034, -1, 'options_options_addpolltimeout_text', 'cphelptext', 'This setting is the number of minutes in which a user may add a poll to a thread he just created. Administrators and moderators with ''caneditpoll'' permission may always add a poll to a thread after creation.', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 0, ''),
