(11036, -1, 'options_options_edittimelimit_text', 'cphelptext', 'This is the time in minutes after the post was posted.  If a user posted a post at 1:00 PM and this setting is set to 5, then that user will not be able to edit that post after 1:05 PM.', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 0, ''),
