(11500, -1, 'repair_list_optimizetables_text', 'cphelptext', 'Database tables should be optimized if you have deleted a large part of a table or if you have made many changes to a table with variable-length rows (tables that have VARCHAR, BLOB, or TEXT columns).  Optimizing helps you reclaim unused space which can reduce the size of your database.', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 0, ''),
