(11556, -1, 'rssposter_edit_titletemplate_text', 'cphelptext', 'The title template controls how thread or announcement titles will appear when items are posted.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou may use any node from the feed XML by entering {feed:<strong>x</strong>} into the template, where ''x'' corresponds to:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>title</li>\r\n<li>description</li>\r\n<li>link</li>\r\n<li>id</li>\r\n<li>date</li>\r\n<li>enclosure_href</li>\r\n<li>content:encoded.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\nFor the most part, you will use {feed:title} to show the title for the current feed item.', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 1193149089, '3.7.0 Beta 1'),
(11557, -1, 'rssposter_edit_titletemplate_title', 'cphelptext', 'Title Template', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 1149682430, '3.6.0 Beta 1'),
(11558, -1, 'rssposter_edit_bodytemplate_text', 'cphelptext', 'The body template controls the main text of threads or announcements for feed items.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn the same way as can be done with the <a href="help.php?do=answer&amp;page=rssposter&amp;pageaction=edit&amp;option=titletemplate">Title Template</a>, you may use selected nodes from the feed XML by specifying {feed:<strong>x</strong>}.<br />\r\nValid values for x include:<br />\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>title</li>\r\n<li>description</li>\r\n<li>link</li>\r\n<li>id</li>\r\n<li>date</li>\r\n<li>enclosure_href</li>\r\n<li>content:encoded.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\nThe main replacements to include in this template is the &lt;description&gt; and &lt;link&gt; nodes, which can be referenced with <strong>{feed:description}</strong> and <strong>{feed:link}</strong>.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFor example:\r\n<pre class="alt2" style="border:inset 1px; padding:4px">[b][i]My RSS Feed[/i] Has Just Posted the Following:[/b]\r\n\r\n<strong style="color:red">{feed:description}</strong>\r\n\r\n[url=&quot;<strong style="color:red">{feed:link}</strong>&quot;]Click here to view the article.[/url]</pre>', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 1193149585, '3.7.0 Beta 1'),
(11559, -1, 'rssposter_edit_bodytemplate_title', 'cphelptext', 'Body Template', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 1149682725, '3.6.0 Beta 1'),
