(11660, -1, 'subscriptions_add_edit_membergroup_text', 'cphelptext', 'If you want this subscription to add users to any secondary groups you can check them here.  When a user purchases this subscription they will be added to these secondary groups.', 'vbulletin', 'Jelsoft', 0, ''),
