(12647, -1, 'blog_admin_modifyfe_bbcode_text', 'cphelptext', 'When disabled, bbcode is stripped, links are replaced with the <strong>[link]</strong> placeholder and attachments are not displayed.\r\n<br /><br />\r\nEnabling full parsing of bbcode and attachments displays the featured entry as it does when opened.  When using a fixed width style, the parsing of bbcode and attachment may stretch the entry so that it flows out of the style.', 'vbblog', 'freddie', 1211321603, '2.0.0 Beta 1'),
