(14153, -1, 'grid_layout_ui_html_incorrect', 'error', 'Could not discern a proper list of widget locations in the Layout Editor UI HTML.<br />\r\nWidget locations need to be in the following format:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>&lt;ul class=&quot;list_no_decoration&quot; id=&quot;widgetlist_column1&quot;&gt;$column[1]&lt;/ul&gt;</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe location may appear any where in the HTML but the first location must start with 1, with each successive column increasing by one, for example:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>&lt;ul class=&quot;list_no_decoration&quot; id=&quot;widgetlist_column1&quot;&gt;$column[1]&lt;/ul&gt;</strong><br />\r\n<strong>&lt;ul class=&quot;list_no_decoration&quot; id=&quot;widgetlist_column1&quot;&gt;$column[2]&lt;/ul&gt;</strong><br />\r\n<strong>&lt;ul class=&quot;list_no_decoration&quot; id=&quot;widgetlist_column1&quot;&gt;$column[3]&lt;/ul&gt;</strong><br />\r\n<strong>&lt;ul class=&quot;list_no_decoration&quot; id=&quot;widgetlist_column1&quot;&gt;$column[4]&lt;/ul&gt;</strong><br />\r\n<strong>&lt;ul class=&quot;list_no_decoration&quot; id=&quot;widgetlist_column1&quot;&gt;$column[5]&lt;/ul&gt;</strong><br />\r\n<br />', 'vbcms', 'Darren', 1237564913, '0.1.0');
